cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.AI, cs.NE 

This paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques for text normalization, which are typically covered under the arXiv sub-categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE). The use of word embeddings is a popular technique in these fields, and the paper's focus on unsupervised learning and domain independence further supports these categories.
